■ Each turn, you may untap this creature the first time it's tapped.
{HUNTING} (While battling, this creature gets +1000 power for each of your Hunters in the battle zone.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}

■ Evolution—Put on one of your Hunters.
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, destroy all creatures except Hunters.
{TRIPLE BREAKER}

■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, search your deck. You may choose a darkness card from it and put it into your graveyard. Then shuffle your deck.
■ Whenever this creature attacks, you may choose a darkness spell that costs 6 or less from your graveyard and cast it for no cost. Then put that spell on the bottom of your deck.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}

■ Evolution: Put on one of your Dragons or Commands.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, you may cast a light or fire spell in your hand for no cost.

{SPEED ATTACKER} (This creature doesn't get summoning sickness.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, untap all cards in your mana zone.
